{"id": 2189, "genre": 1001, "title": "如果学校开设人际关系课堂，你都想学到些什么?", "description": "后来，我总算学会了……为啥非得等到后来？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 2117, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180226143611ycI67xSP5uETKDhZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-26T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 267264, "content": "人与人的关系是怎样形成的？如何做才能关系进一步？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239441}, {"id": 268289, "content": "教一下在社会真正有用的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276040}, {"id": 267266, "content": "跟人相处 怕人发脾气 要怎么破", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1265948}, {"id": 267267, "content": "如何理性处理男女交往等关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271487}, {"id": 267781, "content": "如何与见第一面的朋友聊的开，每次见不熟的人都不知道说什么……尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733402}, {"id": 267271, "content": "对沟通的认识，心理状态的调整，冲突的处理，明白处理好人际关系在情绪和行为的联系。正确看待人与人情绪的不同点", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192775}, {"id": 267527, "content": "如何克服害羞的情绪，交到朋友家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802289}, {"id": 267272, "content": "如果我是特别的，那么特别是什么？如果我是平凡的，那么怎么才叫平凡？", "image": "img/option/option/20180226165842eEwMIpvSBDhozFU4.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716017}, {"id": 267528, "content": "怎么多交不同类型的朋友，以及多跟朋友交流不让朋友烦自己，多学朋友身上的优点来弥补自己身上的不足。", "image": "img/option/option/20180227185257DrVNYjwPUbAy0oKG", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272697}, {"id": 267273, "content": "难道是思想品德升级版？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360615}, {"id": 267274, "content": "不八卦的生存指南", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966973}, {"id": 267275, "content": "怎么做到跟别人在一块的时候不那么尴尬，有话可说", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271514}, {"id": 267276, "content": "如何做一个伪装的坏人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271510}, {"id": 267277, "content": "人際關係是情商的體現！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236958}, {"id": 267789, "content": "和异性第一次见面怎么开口", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1269120}, {"id": 267278, "content": "如何正确地保持理智理解话语的含义……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1214537}, {"id": 267536, "content": "如何把自己的想法表达出来，特别是别人不愿意听的但是正确的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272737}, {"id": 267282, "content": "泡妞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693756}, {"id": 267283, "content": "撩汉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693756}, {"id": 267284, "content": "教会我们如何面对面的时候不会发生尬聊事件，顺便学会如何放下手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461118}, {"id": 267541, "content": "和不喜欢的人或者很喜欢的人如何相处", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272769}, {"id": 267286, "content": "我有一件", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271544}, {"id": 267798, "content": "爱的教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 571811}, {"id": 268313, "content": "不要开设比较好……每个人都八面玲珑左右逢源，这个世界还有真正能互相依靠的人吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251032}, {"id": 267290, "content": "怎么样放开自己 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872723}, {"id": 267292, "content": "怎么和不同的人顺利开启聊天模式", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267168}, {"id": 267293, "content": "有些人的冷漠只是一种保护色，而不是因为对你有恶意，不必惊慌不必怨恨", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144138}, {"id": 267294, "content": "如何分辨一个人是好是坏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271579}, {"id": 267296, "content": "我想有女朋友(滑稽,)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 813730}, {"id": 267299, "content": "一些规则明确一下就可以了，重点是模拟练习", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267980}, {"id": 267300, "content": "如何判断这是否是一段真诚的友谊关系？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271596}, {"id": 267301, "content": "怎样抱着正面心态面在职场上和顾客、上司和同事相处。不用理论，要用实战学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134447}, {"id": 267557, "content": "如何做到在与任何类型的人交谈时保护好自己，但又不会伤害到别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272803}, {"id": 267302, "content": "怎样抱着正面心态面在职场上和顾客、上司和同事相处。不用理论，要用实战学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1134447}, {"id": 267303, "content": "我同学怎么相处", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270682}, {"id": 267304, "content": "尴尬癌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271614}, {"id": 267305, "content": "怎样处理业务伙伴（因工作原因需要结交的人，如：同事）的关系，能够做到及能开展工作，又不过分介入彼此生活。就是如何不与客户天天腻在一起也能麻烦业务。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956627}, {"id": 268073, "content": "怎样把不喜欢交流的人变得不那么讨厌\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198394}, {"id": 267306, "content": "如何保持持续的联络", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898852}, {"id": 267562, "content": "如何处理长辈之间矛盾。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272699}, {"id": 267308, "content": "不要轻易给别人添麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975601}, {"id": 267310, "content": "和朋友交流沟通不要轻易被影响\n也别太过有理智，让别人厌烦\n可能需要学习的就两个字   圆滑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1214744}, {"id": 267566, "content": "为人处事基本礼仪，情商教学，如何换位思考?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003826}, {"id": 267312, "content": "怎么学会聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271672}, {"id": 272944, "content": "怎样不失礼貌又能尽情的表达自己的感受？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297008}, {"id": 267313, "content": "内心太敏感如何和别人相处", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226397}, {"id": 268593, "content": "如何自然的和稀泥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278002}, {"id": 267314, "content": "怎么找到我的男朋友，我是男的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2967}, {"id": 268594, "content": "怎么控制好自己的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278002}, {"id": 267318, "content": "社交能力，情商很重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271698}]}